<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="4Apr1925"><font color="red">4 April 1925</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Robert McAlmon): I have had a relapse since I saw you but am now better so if you have received the proofs of the book I should very much like to revise my contribution now that I am between two operations. On Tuesday or Wednesday of next week (7 or 8 April 1925) I shall probably return to the Clinic &hellip; So please mail me those few pages if you have them </div>
